TopicTitle: 3D internal view of Apollo 11 command module

Articles.Content:
Just found this interactive 3D tour of the interior of the Apollo 11 command module, thought you guys would like;

http://3d.si.edu/apollo11cm/

Very cool.

Like a true steely-eyed-missile-man-wanabe, I had to locate the SCE switch. I see that AUX is the down position.

Haha that's the first thing I looked for as well!

Cheers for the link katateochi
